This Sans is really only possessed in name. Flowey is there, sure, but Sans just doesn't seem to be affected. This is mildly akward for both parties.

The one friendly lnik. He never liked those jock Lniks, with their bows, and swords... UGH! Sanses are all smart scientists, so he just fits right in!

Hailing from a world where the Human-Monster War drove the monsters crazy, this Sans is not to be messed with! He'll give you some chump change he bullied out of the other Sanses if it means you'll leave him alone though.
